- When they sign up, the website says "your profile has been reviewed"

### Verification Data Requirements
| Data                                | Why                     |
| ----------------------------------- | ----------------------- |
| Full name                           | Identification          |
| Date of birth (year only)           | Age gating              |
| Email + mobile                      | Contact                 |
| Home town / county                  | Consistency             |
| Two independent references          | Identity confidence     |
| Social account link (LinkedIn etc.) | Public verification     |
| Live video introduction call        | Liveness / person match |
| Signed declaration                  | Legal accountability    | (Anisha needs to get form OR AI and anisha approve)

### Data Retention
| Data             | Retention              |
| ---------------- | ---------------------- |
| Application data | While active + 2 years |
| Rejected         | 6 months               |
| Call notes       | 6 months               |

